{"tid":1804774,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"利物浦不敗奪冠？奧雲：絕對可以","createTime":"2019-12-31T08:35:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T14:16:31.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"fe453802d773fc6cf01ea89a01f611a26dcfb3e7","tid":1804774,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T08:35:46.000Z","msg":"前利物浦前鋒奧雲認為，紅軍是本季英超最佳球隊，遠勝其他競爭對手，可以保持不敗勇奪隊史首座英超獎盃，甚至可超越曼城的100分奪標分數。<br />\n<br />\n利物浦本季實在出色，狂風掃落葉征服英超，開季18勝1和只失2分，先後雙殺李斯特城及擊敗曼城，現已大幅領先次席李城13分並少賽1場。奧雲認為英超獎盃是利物浦的囊中物：「利物浦可奪英超冠軍，並可超越曼城100分積分紀錄。」<br />\n<br />\n「我看不到他們為何不能辦到，利物浦本季演出遠超所有對手，他們絕對有力全季保不敗。若利物浦可以保持多1季或2季這樣的高水準，紅軍或許就是英超史上最強球隊。」(<a href=\"http://goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoal.com&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJqDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=0aa3f099\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"6dee23cac1efeadc83a017a0299ab403a0f08260","tid":1804774,"uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T08:36:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/227003e6b9e634dde42054fd4155c98e/42d2af8ce25df0d4-10/s500x750/92189de68bd6b01e4bf2c16db24a78f925c3bd59.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F227003e6b9e634dde42054fd4155c98e%2F42d2af8ce25df0d4-10%2Fs500x750%2F92189de68bd6b01e4bf2c16db24a78f925c3bd59.gifv&h=2fda0cd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/2147c69ca9e13964b426c8d18d656dd2/42d2af8ce25df0d4-7e/s500x750/1db75132cb0cd9a8b89a22181f7220c86d5d7e51.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F2147c69ca9e13964b426c8d18d656dd2%2F42d2af8ce25df0d4-7e%2Fs500x750%2F1db75132cb0cd9a8b89a22181f7220c86d5d7e51.gifv&h=6b1821ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20ee8c825302c4d330ba8ace62e136528984b267","tid":1804774,"uid":108201,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019